# itch-css
The custom CSS I use on itch.io.

## [Profile page](https://javacakegames.itch.io/)

Pale Ukraine flag background. Temporary, during 2022 Russian invasion. Use with white background.

```css
.user_page_wrap::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: url("data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMjAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjgwMCIgcHJlc2VydmVBc3BlY3RSYXRpbz0ibm9uZSI+DQo8cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTIwMCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI4MDAiIGZpbGw9IiMwMDVCQkIiLz4NCjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMjAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjQwMCIgeT0iNDAwIiBmaWxsPSIjRkZENTAwIi8+DQo8L3N2Zz4NCg==");
  background-size: 100% 100%;
  opacity: 10%;
  background-attachment: fixed;
  pointer-events: none;
}
```

Make "GIF" notice less prominent so as to obscure the game cover images a little less.

```css
.gif_label {
  top: 0 !important;
  left: 0 !important;
  border-radius: 0 0 8px 0 !important;
}
```

Move "supported by" section to the end of the page.

```css
.user_page {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.purchased_games {
  order: 9;
}
```

## [Bun Run](https://javacakegames.itch.io/bun-run)

Apply nearest-neighbour scaling to images.

```css
.custom-pixel {
  image-rendering: pixelated;
}
```

## [GBTK Sort](https://javacakegames.itch.io/gbtk-sort)

Slowly pans the page background, among other things.

```css
ul {
  margin: 0;
}

#wrapper {
  animation: custom-bg 150s linear infinite;
}

#inner_column {
  overflow: visible;
}

.custom-hans:hover {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 9999999999;
  animation: custom-hans-anim 3s;
  user-drag: none;
  -webkit-user-drag: none;
}

@keyframes custom-hans-anim {
  from {
    transform: scale(1);
  }
  to {
    transform: scale(10);
    opacity: 0;
    display: none;
  }
}

@keyframes custom-bg {
  from { background-position: 2722px 0; }
  to { background-position: 0 0; }
}

@media (min-width: 1001px) {
  .custom-version-table {
    width: 920px;
  }
}
```

## [Ghostta Go!](https://javacakegames.itch.io/ghostta)

Adds subtly-animated text above the game in a custom font. Also classes that are displayed only on PC or mobile respectively.

```css
#header::before {
  content: 'Ghostta Go!';
  display: block;
  margin-top: 20px;
  font-family: ghosties !important;
  font-size: 4em;
  text-align: center;
  font-weight: normal !important;
  margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  animation: custom-breathe 30s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

.custom-mobile {
  display: none;
}
.custom-pc {
  display: block;
}
@media only screen and (hover: none) and (pointer: coarse) {
  .custom-mobile {
    display: block;
  }
  .custom-pc {
    display: none;
  }
}

@keyframes custom-breathe {
  from { letter-spacing: 0em; }
  to { letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
}

@font-face {
    font-family: 'ghosties';
    src: url(data:application/font-woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff2');
    font-weight: normal;
    font-style: normal;
}
```

## [Just Wizards](https://javacakegames.itch.io/just-wizards)

Various animations and Easter eggs. Not stuff you'd want to do on a serious page!

```css
figcaption {
  margin-top: -1.25em;
  font-size: .75em;
}

a {
  text-decoration: underline wavy;
}

.game_pending {
  border-radius: 50%;
}

.post_date::after {
  content: ' anno Domini';
}

.icon-tux::before {
  font-size: 1.5em;
  line-height: 50%;
}

.icon-tux:hover::before {
  content: 'üêß';
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
  .load_iframe_btn {
    animation: youdBetterRun 1s ease-out alternate infinite;
  }
  .screenshot_list:hover {
    transform: rotate(7deg);
  }
  .custom-wizards {
    animation: slide 5s linear infinite;
  }
  .custom-reduced-motion {
    display: none;
  }
}

.load_iframe_btn {
  cursor: zoom-in !important;
}

@keyframes youdBetterRun {
  from {
    transform: scale(1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 #000;
  }
  to {
    transform: scale(2);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12.5px 2.5px #222;
  }
}

.inner_column {
  overflow: visible;
}

.screenshot_list {
  transform: rotate(-7deg);
  transition: transform 7s;
}

@keyframes slide {
  from { background-position-y: 0; }
  to { background-position-y: 200px; }
}

.custom-left {
  left: 0;
}

.custom-right {
  right: 0;
  transform: scaleX(-1); 
  animation-direction: reverse !important;
}

.avatar_container img {
  display: none !important;
}

.avatar_container {
  background: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
  background-size: 100%;
}

@media (min-width: 1240px) {
  .custom-wizards {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;

    height: 100%;

    z-index: 1;

  }
}
```

## [Sinking City Saviour](https://javacakegames.itch.io/sinking-city)

Improvements to development log pages. itch.io doesn't handle embeds well on mobile, for example.

```css
.responsive .inner_column {
  max-width: 1440px;
}

/* https://embedresponsively.com/ */
.custom-fourThree {
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 75%;
  height: 0; overflow:
  hidden;
  max-width: 100%;
}

.custom-fourThree iframe,
.custom-fourThree object,
.custom-fourThree embed,
.custom-fourThree img {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}
```
